01:51:49.580 --> 01:51:51.810
I'm gonna ask your wife a couple
of questions. okay?

954
01:51:51.910 --> 01:51:54.850
You move...

955
01:51:54.950 --> 01:51:56.980
<i>you make one sound...</i>

956
01:51:57.090 --> 01:52:00.180
