He knows what I'm talking about.
$2.5 million. That's what Victor got. isn't it?

966
01:52:37.490 --> 01:52:40.490
- What are you talking about?
- 2.5 million.

967
01:52:40.600 --> 01:52:42.890
<i>2.5 million to your lawyer
Jordan Kalfus...</i>

968
01:52:43.000 --> 01:52:46.130
that he put in an account in the Cayman
Islands. but he won't get a chance to spend it.

969
01:52:49.470 --> 01:52:51.800
What happened to the other five. Sam?

970
01:52:51.910 --> 01:52:54.840
<i>Huh? That's 2.5. 2.5.
What is five from 10?</i>

971
01:52:54.940 --> 01:52:57.470
That's five. What happened
to the other five. Sam? Tell your wife.

972
01:52:57.580 --> 01:53:00.010
<i>- It's your chance to talk.
What happened to the other five?</i>

973
01:53:00.120 --> 01:53:01.480
- You got a wife. Creasy?
- No. I don't have a wife.

974
01:53:01.580 --> 01:53:04.350
Then you'll never know how hard
it could be to tell your wife the truth.

975
01:53:04.450 --> 01:53:06.680
No. you have a wife!
You tell me what happened!

976
01:53:06.790 --> 01:53:08.920
It was in this room
that my father prayed.

977
01:53:09.020 --> 01:53:11.720
- I don't give a fuck about your fucking father!
- My father prayed.

978
01:53:11.830 --> 01:53:15.730
<i>He prayed that his gambling debts and his
infidelities would be forgiven right in this room.</i>

979
01:53:15.830 --> 01:53:18.530
<i>- Samuel! I love you!
- What. Lisa?</i>

980
01:53:18.630 --> 01:53:22.430
<i>- Tell me the truth.
- I didn't inherit a kingdom! That's the truth!</i>

981
01:53:22.540 --> 01:53:25.440
You wanna know the truth?
I inherited his debt and his mess.

982
01:53:25.540 --> 01:53:28.440
- I inherited his lawyer Jordan...
- You tell me what happened to my baby!

983
01:53:28.540 --> 01:53:31.100
Say it! Say it! Say it!

984
01:53:31.210 --> 01:53:33.840
Say it! Say it! Be a fucking man!

985
01:53:35.850 --> 01:53:38.290
Jordan told me she'd sit in a room...

986
01:53:38.390 --> 01:53:40.790
and watch cartoons all day...

987
01:53:40.890 --> 01:53:43.760
and she'd eat ice cream
and we'd have her back in two days.

988
01:53:43.860 --> 01:53:46.460
He lied to me!

989
01:53:46.560 --> 01:53:49.430
That's why he's fucking dead!
I did it!

990
01:53:49.530 --> 01:53:51.590
I did it. Lisa!

991
01:53:51.700 --> 01:53:54.430
I agreed to the kidnapping.

992
01:53:54.540 --> 01:53:57.970
I did it for us...
for the three of us.

993
01:54:06.420 --> 01:54:08.540
I'm so sorry. Lisa.

994
01:54:14.560 --> 01:54:16.530
You kill him.

995
01:54:17.930 --> 01:54:19.830
You kill him or I will.

996
01:54:50.190 --> 01:54:52.160
Huh. You know. they say a. um...

997
01:54:54.570 --> 01:54:57.690
<i>a bullet always tells the truth.</i>

998
01:55:06.980 --> 01:55:08.950
It never lies.

999
01:55:21.930 --> 01:55:26.190
It didn't work for me. Samuel. but maybe...

1000
01:55:28.470 --> 01:55:31.030
Maybe it'll work for you.

1001
01:55:40.340 --> 01:55:42.940
<i>I'll pray for you.</i>

1002
01:58:45.400 --> 01:58:47.300
<i>Gracias.</i>

1003
01:59:09.790 --> 01:59:11.690
- Hola?
- Hola.

1004
01:59:11.790 --> 01:59:14.280
<i>- Mr. Creasy?
- Yeah. it's me.</i>

1005
01:59:14.390 --> 01:59:18.450
<i>- I traced the PIN for you and I have an address.
- Yeah?</i>

1006
