<i>She lives in Los Arcos.
apartment 26D. Via Appia.</i>

1008
01:59:26.510 --> 01:59:28.970
<i>- Good.
- And another thing.</i>

1009
01:59:29.080 --> 01:59:32.880
<i>Pick up today's paper and you'll have
a picture of âThe Voice. "</i>

1010
01:59:32.980 --> 01:59:34.950
<i>Good. Thank you.</i>

1011
02:00:37.940 --> 02:00:40.040
Shh. shh. shh.

1012
02:01:43.510 --> 02:01:45.440
<i>Jose? Que te pasa?</i>

1013
02:03:00.520 --> 02:03:02.350
<i>Si­.</i>

1014
02:03:02.460 --> 02:03:04.420
Okay.

1015
