<i>Si­.</i>

1018
02:03:34.850 --> 02:03:36.850
Okay. Uh...

1019
02:03:41.190 --> 02:03:43.090
<i>- Si­?
- Si­.</i>

1020
02:03:50.300 --> 02:03:52.930
Aurelio Rosas Sanchez. Okay.

1021
